== Data services queried at runtime ==

SponsorBlock — community-sourced sponsor-segment data.
When sponsor-skip is enabled, TL;DW performs read-only segment lookups against
the public SponsorBlock API (https://sponsor.ajay.app). It does not bundle,
mirror, or redistribute the SponsorBlock database. The SponsorBlock segment
database is made available under the Open Database License (ODbL) and
Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0);
attribution is given here and the NonCommercial term applies to the data.
SponsorBlock is a project by Ajay Ramachandran and contributors.
https://sponsor.ajay.app/

== Third-party services accessed with the user's own credentials ==

The AI destinations — Google Gemini, OpenAI ChatGPT, Anthropic Claude, and
Google NotebookLM — are independent third-party services. TL;DW accesses them
through the user's own signed-in account (open-in-a-tab mode) or the user's own
API key (Direct API mode). They are not bundled with, endorsed by, or
affiliated with TL;DW. Their respective terms and privacy policies apply.
